      { "@type": "Question", "name": "What are the biggest LMS trends in 2026?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Seven key trends: 1) AI moving from feature to foundation, 2) Customer education going mainstream, 3) Market consolidation accelerating (Coursera-Udemy $2.5B merger), 4) Mobile learning reaching maturity, 5) Micro-credentials gaining institutional acceptance, 6) Community becoming a core LMS feature, 7) Video evolving from lectures to interactive experiences." } },
